html.body: CYCLIN A module Cyclin A2 binds to and activates the cyclin-dependent kinases CDK2. The activity of the complex rises at the end of G1 phase and drops at metaphase (PMID:15840442). At the G2/M transition, both E2F1 and DP1 are phosphorylated by CycA2/CDK2 in the active E2F1/DP1/PCAF complex (PMID:16135794). Activation of CycA2/CDK2 leads to the end of E2F1-mediated transcription (PMID:15840440).
